    "The red, solid line shows the difference in performance for the context condition.",
    "The circles show the F score by language for the translations, the squares show the F score for the original scores.",
    "In this study, we investigated OpenAIs GPT-3.5 and GPT-4s ability to fact-check claims.",
    "We found that GPT-4 outperformed GPT-3.5.",
    "Notably, even without contextual information, GPT-3.5 and GPT-4 demonstrate good performance of 63-75% accuracy on average, which further improves to above 80 and 89% for non-ambiguous verdicts when context is incorporated."
